        <p id="Par48">Our univariate and bivariate power calculation results under the variance components model (VCM) framework appear in Fig.Â <xref rid="Fig3" ref-type="fig">3</xref>. (We used the Julia Plots package to obtain all our graphs.) In the univariate model, <inline-formula id="IEq35"><alternatives><tex-math id="M77">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
